<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-6xl">
  <div class="text-center mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
      <img src="/icon.png" alt="Japanese Walking" class="w-20 h-20 mr-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Japanese Walking</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">インターバル速歩で健康習慣を身につけよう</p>
  </div>

  <% if @current_session %>
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900">現在のセッション進行中</h2>
          <p class="text-blue-700 mt-1">開始時刻: <%= @current_session.started_at.strftime("%H:%M") %></p>
        </div>
        <%= link_to "セッションを続ける", walking_session_path(@current_session), 
            class: "bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <%= link_to new_walking_session_path, 
          class: "inline-block bg-green-600 text-white text-xl px-12 py-6 rounded-full hover:bg-green-700 transition transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg" do %>
        <span class="flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
          ウォーキングを開始
        </span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="mb-12" data-controller="weekly-progress">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">今週の進捗</h2>
    <div data-weekly-progress-target="progress" class="mb-6"></div>
    <div data-weekly-progress-target="stats"></div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 mt-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">日別活動</h3>
      <div data-weekly-progress-target="chart"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow">
    <div class="px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">最近のセッション</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
      <% @walking_sessions.each do |session| %>
        <%= link_to session, class: "block px-6 py-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition cursor-pointer" do %>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                <%= session.started_at.strftime("%Y年%m月%d日 %H:%M") %>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-1 flex items-center space-x-4">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">
                  <%= session.duration_in_minutes %> 分
                </span>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                  <%= session.calculate_distance_from_points.round(2) %> km
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium 
                       <%= session.status == 'completed' ? 'bg-green-100 text-green-800' : 'bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800' %>">
                  <%= session.status == 'completed' ? '完了' : session.status %>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">インターバル速歩とは？</h3>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
      <p>🏃 3分間の速歩き + 🚶 3分間のゆっくり歩きを交互に5セット</p>
      <p>⏱️ 合計30分のウォーキング</p>
      <p>📅 週4日以上の実施が目標</p>
      <p>💪 筋力・持久力の向上と生活習慣病の予防に効果的</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        ※ 「<a href="https://www.shinshu-u.ac.jp/zukan/cooperation/i-walk.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">インターバル速歩</a>」はNPO法人熟年体育大学リサーチセンターの登録商標です。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>